\small{
Detail-oriented Physics graduate with a strong interest in IT governance, cybersecurity risk management, and regulatory compliance within financial services. Experienced in analytical problem solving, technical documentation, evidence collection, and working with sensitive information. Familiar with information security principles, operating systems, and structured reporting. Motivated to support governance, risk, audit, and compliance activities within a global organisation.
}

